headline: United Airlines Holdings, Inc. (UAL) Extends Special Olympics Service Ambassador Program
summary: United Airlines Holdings, Inc. (NASDAQ:UAL) is included in our list of the 10 Cheap Travel Stocks to Buy According to Analysts. On July 18, 2025, United Airlines Holdings, Inc. (NASDAQ:UAL) announced that it is planning to extend its Special Olympics Service Ambassador (SOSA) program with the hiring of 28 ambassadors at all seven U.S. hubs. […]
